OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a chilly start it will be
OL,6,Flargely dry with bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells throughout the day. Chance of a
OL,8,Ffew well scattered light showers
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Breezy along the
OL,10,Fcoasts. Slightly milder inland than
OL,11,Frecent days.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny daytime showers soon
OL,14,Ffading this evening to leave a dry
OL,15,Fnight, with some lengthy clear spells.
OL,16,FTurning chilly, with patchy frost in
OL,17,Fprone rural spots, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
